title: Sample Book, American Futures III, 1956
description: Designs by several well-known artists, including Courtyard, Courtyard Texture, and possibly Doorway, Beach, and Paper Butterflies by Ilonka Karasz; Shells & Rope by Marion Dorn, Mangoes by Lanette Scheeline. Also includes designs by William Justema, Zue Martin, Tina Leser Workshop and others.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, American Futures III, 1956; Designed by Ilonka Karasz, William Justema, Marion Dorn Kauffer, Zue Martin and Lanette Scheeline; USA; intaglio-printed paper; plastic coated; Overall: 52.5 x 53.5cm (20 11/16 x 21 1/16in.); 1980-77-4-1/86
